<item>
            <title>[FLINK-19868] Csv Serialization schema contains line delimiter</title>
                <link>https://issues.apache.org/jira/browse/FLINK-19868</link>
                <project id="12315522" key="FLINK">Flink</project>
                    <description>&lt;p&gt;CsvRowSerializationSchema.serialize(Row.of(&quot;f0&quot;, &quot;f1&quot;)) =&amp;gt; f0,f1\n&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;Csv Serialization schema is for one line, why contains line delimiter?&lt;/p&gt;</description>
